  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To determine the applicability and utility of Gerd Q in the diagnosis of GERD and assessment of treatment response</measure>
    <time_frame>The applicability and utility of the Gerd Questionnaire will be done on 2 vists- Day 1 and Day 30</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>To assess and monitor the treatment response of patients diagnosed with GERD</measure>
